Any co-req (I/W) unit in {EDF5513, EDF5514, EDF5515, EDF5516}

description: This is a unit for professional experience in psychology. Students complete the required number of supervised days and the activities specified in the professional experience manual for this unit. Students' learning is supported by professional experience advisers. This unit tracks the requirements for completing professional experience in the course. This unit is designed to support psychological training on a 5+1 basis.
